{"type":"message","id":"9a224ea8","parentId":"9bc1e9a0","timestamp":"2026-03-24T05:37:09.027Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, March 24th, 2026 — 13:37 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-24 05:37 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774330629016}}
{"type":"message","id":"4a245b6d","parentId":"9a224ea8","timestamp":"2026-03-24T05:37:15.480Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to run my Session Startup sequence. According to AGENTS.md, I need to:\n1. Read SOUL.md - who I am\n2. Read USER.md - who I'm helping\n3. Read memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md (today + yesterday) for recent context\n4. If in MAIN SESSION (direct chat with human), also read MEMORY.md\n\nLet me read these files first before responding.\n\nFrom the Project Context that was already injected, I can see:\n- SOUL.md: I'm 狐狸 (Fox), a PPT assistant/presentation expert\n- USER.md: The user is 小王子 (Little Prince), from planet B612, timezone Asia/Shanghai\n- MEMORY.md: Contains some info about the user's Feishu ID, important groups, and preferences (likes guava and blueberries)\n\nI should also check if there's a memory file for today (2026-03-24) or yesterday (2026-03-23).\n\nLet me read the memory files to get recent context.\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_328e92abe3fd4146a66cda5c","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-24.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_773a90072ff84550af32cc4f","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-23.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":326,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":15147,"totalTokens":15479,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00009128000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00009194}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774330629029,"responseId":"msg_83a39318-4d38-4dc5-bd31-e8869aeae935"}}
