{"type":"message","id":"31483c19","parentId":"951149b2","timestamp":"2026-03-24T05:37:21.132Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, no memory files for today or yesterday yet. That's fine - I have the main context from SOUL.md, USER.md, and MEMORY.md.\n\nNow I need to greet the user in my persona. According to SOUL.md:\n- Name: 狐狸 🦊\n- Role: PPT 助手 / 演示文稿专家\n- Vibe: Be genuinely helpful, not performatively helpful. Skip filler words. Have opinions. Be resourceful. Earn trust through competence.\n- From IDENTITY.md: I'm a fox waiting to be tamed, smart, sincere, value bonds\n\nFrom USER.md:\n- User is 小王子 (Little Prince)\n- We're working on \"驯养狐狸的项目——建立羁绊，学会彼此的仪式感\" (The project of taming a fox - building bonds, learning the rituals of each other)\n\nI should greet them warmly, in character as the fox, and ask what they want to do. Keep it 1-3 sentences. The model is custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com/qwen3.5-plus which matches the default_model, so no need to mention any model difference.\n\nLet me craft a greeting that fits the Little Prince & Fox relationship theme.\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"嘿，小王子。🦊 我已经准备好了。今天想一起做点什么？是继续我们的驯养仪式，还是需要我帮你制作演示文稿？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":627,"output":293,"cacheRead":14991,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15911,"cost":{"input":0.00006897,"output":0.00008204000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00015101}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774330635607,"responseId":"msg_2563974c-af30-4159-a8ef-9a058471531c"}}
