{"type":"message","id":"6eb0c378","parentId":"10dcca59","timestamp":"2026-03-24T05:37:45.709Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"小王子想要查看他的电脑配置。我需要使用 exec 命令来运行系统命令获取电脑配置信息。在 Linux 系统上，常用的命令包括：\n- uname -a 获取系统信息\n- cat /etc/os-release 获取操作系统版本\n- lscpu 或 cat /proc/cpuinfo 获取 CPU 信息\n- free -h 获取内存信息\n- df -h 获取磁盘空间\n- lspci 或 lsusb 获取硬件设备\n\n我会组合几个命令来获取全面的配置信息。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_eef561c0e2504007babd1493","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 系统信息 ===\" && uname -a && echo -e \"\\n=== 操作系统 ===\" && cat /etc/os-release | head -5 && echo -e \"\\n=== CPU 信息 ===\" && lscpu | grep -E \"Model name|CPU\\(s\\)|Architecture\" && echo -e \"\\n=== 内存信息 ===\" && free -h && echo -e \"\\n=== 磁盘空间 ===\" && df -h / /home 2>/dev/null | head -5 && echo -e \"\\n=== GPU 信息 ===\" && lspci | grep -i vga 2>/dev/null || echo \"未检测到独立显卡\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":992,"output":279,"cacheRead":14991,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16262,"cost":{"input":0.00010912000000000001,"output":0.00007812,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00018724000000000003}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774330659404,"responseId":"msg_89523cb0-dd3d-4d32-9bcb-40fee9588c75"}}
